|}{{#ifeq:{{{subobjects|yes}}}|yes|
{{Category/subobjects | category={{{category|}}} | page={{{page|{{FULLPAGENAME}}}}} }}|}}</includeonly><noinclude>
Closes a SemanticSchemas sidebox opened by `Category/sidebox-header`.
Same footer behavior as `Category/table-footer` — kept as a separate
template so sidebox and table chrome can diverge without coupling.

Parameters:
* category        - The category name. Required.
* page            - Target page for subobjects lookup. Defaults to
                    {{FULLPAGENAME}}.
* backlinks       - "no" to suppress the backlinks row.
* subobjects      - "no" to suppress the nested Category/subobjects
                    block.
* backlink_section - Pre-baked backlinks wikitext; used in place of
                    the dynamic Category/render-reverse lookup when set.
</noinclude>
